Ywak jo-Israel e tuech Babulon


1  Ne wabet piny e bath aore mag Babulon,

mi waywak ka waparo Sayun.


2  Ne wang’awo thumbewa e yien man kanyo


3  Joma ne omakowa ne owachonwa mondo wawernigi wend Sayun.


4  To ere kaka dwawer wend Ruoth Nyasaye e piny jomoko nono?


5  Kapo ni wiya nyalo wil kodi, yaye Jerusalem,

to onego bada ma agoyogo thum, tal.


6  Ee, ka ok apari,

kendo ka ok aparo ni in e morna maduong’,

to lewa mondo omok e danda!


7  A Ruoth Nyasaye, parie gima ne jo-Edom otimo,

chieng’ mane okaw Jerusalem!

Adier, ne gisiko giwacho niya,

“Mukeuru mondo oruombre piny!”


8  

In Babulon bende ibiro kethi,

kendo ng’at ma ochuloni kuor kuom gik ma isetimonwa

en jahawi!


9  Ee, ng’at mokawo nyithindi, mochwado e lwanda

en jahawi!

